{"created": "2026-03-16T20:56:42.043618", "current_version": "1.0.0", "project": "ESP32 Distance Sensor", "versions": {"1.0.0": {"created": "2026-03-16T20:56:42.043616", "creator": {"program": "sphinx_needs", "version": "7.0.0"}, "needs": {"SPEC_ARCH_MEMORY_1": {"acceptance_criteria": "", "api_signature": "", "arch": {}, "avatar": null, "closed_at": null, "completion": null, "component": "", "constraints": [], "constraints_error": null, "constraints_passed": true, "constraints_results": {}, "content": "**Description:** Memory managed with FreeRTOS heap and ESP-IDF capabilities.\n\n**Allocation Strategy:**\n\n- **Static**: Component structures at compile time (predictable)\n- **Dynamic**: Runtime allocations use ``heap_caps_malloc()``\n- **DMA Buffers**: Use ``MALLOC_CAP_DMA`` capability\n- **IRAM**: Use ``IRAM_ATTR`` only for time-critical ISRs\n\n**Memory Configuration:**\n\n- 4MB flash (CONFIG_ESPTOOLPY_FLASHSIZE_4MB)\n- ~41% free flash after base system\n- Monitor: ``esp_get_free_heap_size()``\n\n**Design Principle**: Prefer static allocation for predictable memory usage", "created_at": null, "docname": "12_design/spec_high_level_architecture", "doctype": ".rst", "duration": null, "external_css": "external_link", "external_url": null, "has_dead_links": false, "has_forbidden_dead_links": false, "header_file": "", "id": "SPEC_ARCH_MEMORY_1", "id_prefix": null, "is_external": false, "is_import": false, "is_modified": false, "jinja_content": false, "layout": null, "lineno": 399, "links": ["REQ_SYS_HW_1"], "links_back": [], "max_amount": null, "max_content_lines": null, "modifications": 0, "parameters": "", "params": null, "parent_need": null, "parent_needs": [], "parent_needs_back": [], "parts": {}, "post_content": null, "post_template": null, "pre_content": null, "pre_template": null, "prefix": null, "priority": "", "query": null, "rationale": "", "returns": "", "section_name": "Threading Architecture", "sections": ["Threading Architecture", "High-Level Architecture Design Specification"], "service": null, "signature": null, "specific": null, "status": "approved", "style": null, "tags": ["memory", "performance"], "template": null, "title": "Memory Management Strategy", "type": "spec", "type_name": "Design Specification", "updated_at": null, "url": null, "url_postfix": null, "user": null}}, "needs_amount": 1}}}